            "title": "中國有色金屬工業協會呼籲對銅等大宗金屬考慮設立產能上限",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國主要金屬行業協會表示，中國應對國內銅、鋅、鉛考慮設立產能上限，以應對國內的惡性競爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國有色金屬工業協會周四在季度新聞發布會後發布聲明，督促借鑒電解鋁經驗，對銅、鉛、鋅等大宗金屬嚴控新增產能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著國內銅冶煉企業警告「內卷式」競爭導致銅精礦加工費降至歷史性低位，威脅行業健康發展，該協會上個月表示，已向國家相關部門報送嚴控銅冶煉產能擴張的具體措施建議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為全球最大的工業金屬生產國，中國經歷數年的產能擴張後，正大力遏製鋼鐵和太陽能等關鍵行業的過度競爭。產能擴張已削弱了企業的盈利能力，加劇了這個亞洲最大經濟體根深蒂固的通縮壓力，而且當前中國還在努力應對與美國的貿易戰並扭轉房地產市場下滑。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-df7b24fe-69d7-33ea-a1c9-7f0e26eaaf15-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">協會表示，這種「內卷式」競爭削弱了企業在原料採購方面的話語權，使行業整體利潤空間收窄，影響可持續發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’a Top Metals Group Calls for Ceiling on Copper Capacity</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
